{"id": "1459717069464539330", "channel_id": "1459717069464539330", "type": 0, "author_id": "330867601691639809", "author_name": "rain_scarlet", "author_bot": false, "content": "Francis\n\nRealm: Ultra\nType: Assault\nBirthday: ####\nGender: Female\nNous index: 37\nBased on: Hound of Tindalos\n\n\n\nStats: \nCon: 115\nAtk: 155\nDef: 105\nNo Psyche Surge: 【12 Realm Mastery】 【9.6% Damage Amp】\nPsyche Surge +12: 【36 Realm Mastery】【28.8% Damage Amp】\n\nTalent:\n【Hunt Across Time】: Whenever Poison is Triggered on an enemy on your turn from other sources that is not【Time-Rend Hounds】, Francis commands all【Time-Rend Hounds】to pursuit the enemy, each dealing damage equal to 20% of Francis's ATK and trigger 10% of total poison on the enemy. \n\n\n【Soulforge Aplitude】: Poison applied by all ally awakeners are increased by 10~30%. Francis's final damage against Ultra enemies is increased by 20~50%. \n\nSkills\n\nExalt \n【Agent of the Hounds】: Francis summons 2【Time-Rend Hounds】. Deal damage to all enemies equal to 240% of Francis's Atk, apply the same amount of poison and put a copy of【Chrono pursuit】with fleeting into your hand. \n\nOver-Exalt\n【Eternal Hunt】: Summon 5【Time-Rend Hounds】instead.", "timestamp": "2026-01-11T01:14:29.592000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 8}, {"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1459717069464539330", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Awakener Kit Speculation: Francis", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1441261039227240468"]}
{"id": "1459717423828828261", "channel_id": "1459717069464539330", "type": 0, "author_id": "330867601691639809", "author_name": "rain_scarlet", "author_bot": false, "content": "Rouse\n【Acute Traveler】（3 cost): Francis gains 50 aliemus. Rouse: Damage from Francis's Quasar effect is doubled and summons 1 【Time-Rend Hounds】.\n\n\n【Chrono Pursuit 】(1 cost）: Deal damage to all enemies equal to 20% of Francis's Atk, apply the same amount of poison. Then trigger 30% of Poison on all enemies. Quasar: Deal damage to all enemies equal to 80% of Francis's ATK, and apply the same amount of poison.\n\n\n【Precision Surgery】(3 cost): Select 2 cards from the draw pile, discard them, and put a copy of them into Ultra space. Gain 10 aliemus and Summon a【Time-Rend Hounds】for each card in Ultra space. Quasar: Deal damage to all enemies equal to 80% of Francis's ATK, and apply the same amount of poison.\n\n\n\n【Strike】(1 cost): Deal damage equal to 20% of Francis's Atk. Francis gain 10 aliemus. Quasar: Deal damage to all enemies equal to 80% of Francis's ATK, and apply the same amount of poison.\n\n\n【Defence】(1 cost): Gain shield equal to 20% of Francis's Def. Francis gain 10 aliemus. Quasar: Deal damage to all enemies equal to 80% of Francis's ATK, and apply the same amount of poison.\n\n\n\nEnlighten:\n\nE1【Hellhound】: For every 1% Damage Amp Francis and her equipped WoD & Covenant have，her Crit rate and Crit Damage is increased by 0.5%. 25% of all damage dealt by【Time-Rend Hounds】are also Inflicted as poison.\n\nE2【Twisted Love】: When you annihilate a card from ultra space, the next Francis's card you play can trigger Quasar again. Upon entering ultra space, give “Trigger 10% of all enemies poison” effect to the card.\n\nE3【Unconditional Sacrifice】: 【Chrono Pursuit】also inflicts vulnerability to all enemies for 1 turn. At the start of battle, draw a【Precision Surgery 】and reduce its cost by 1.", "timestamp": "2026-01-11T01:15:54.079000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-11T01:48:09.934000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1459717069464539330", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Awakener Kit Speculation: Francis", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1441261039227240468"]}
{"id": "1459717593303744684", "channel_id": "1459717069464539330", "type": 0, "author_id": "330867601691639809", "author_name": "rain_scarlet", "author_bot": false, "content": "WoD\n\n【Repentance of a Mother】\n\nAttributes without ascension:\nDamage Amp  14.4%\nAttributes with 12 ascension:\nDamage Amp  28.8%\n\nEffect:\nUser's base damage and poison application is increased by 20%. User gains 35% increased crit rate and crit damage against poisoned targets. Whenever Poison is Triggered, the user gains shield equal to 7% of your team's max health. This effect can only trigger once per turn.\n\n\n\nPosse\n\n【Second Chance】: Pursuit damage gains 15% Crit rate and Crit Damage for this turn. If Francis is in the team, also draw a copy of 【Chrono Pursuit 】.", "timestamp": "2026-01-11T01:16:34.485000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-11T01:16:55.809000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1459717069464539330", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Awakener Kit Speculation: Francis", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1441261039227240468"]}
